description:
The tenth collection. The special collection. This is art. This is satire.

This is one of the first "Art Satire" - Projects in the Cryptospace.

This "Renkert Snofla"-Collection again shows the development from the Basic picture without many effects to the final picture of this collection wich has lots of artefacts and effects.

24 Steps - 24 beautiful unique pictures. But wait.. Every picture contains 9 RENKERT! 9 Pictures in one!

Yes this was a lot of work!

Check out the details of the final version!

The way of creation is the artists secret.

This is the tenth collection. Others will follow. Maybe. Or not?! Every collection could be the final one!
name: Renkert Snofla - The tenth collection
